{"tid":391852,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"平行時空另一端既海洋公園","createTime":"2017-09-08T05:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T05:34:29.000Z","uid":144018,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eedbcf8dd26321c2093b85266fcc29a0e6fd826","tid":391852,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/133813_0143afdc4f3c748c9632bfaa255e818d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F133813_0143afdc4f3c748c9632bfaa255e818d.png&h=171b7174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信唔少巴絲都鐘意去海記,貪佢又平又抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要刺激有機動遊戲、要可愛既有動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n很滿足了吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ? 少年你太年輕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟本住有前無後、打死罷就既精神,搵到當年海記擴建最玨本既構思仲將佢還原番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發現當年擴建既構思簡直係so exciting !<br />\n<br />\n小弟決定公諸同好,實行每個Happy Friday帶大家遊海洋公園！<br />\n仲要係遊一個處於平行時空既海洋公園，一個自己去唔到既海洋公園～<br />\n所以記得要跟實我哋「完不了的擴建 － 海洋公園重新發展計劃」系列<br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://TourisMan.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTourisMan.hk&d=ZYEtvT0CK1NF